sub_title: Process Optimization Lead at Elsevier / Elevate coach
summary:
*      10+ years of experience in business development, product development & project/process management in scientific publishing industry.
*	10+ years of experience conducting quantitative analysis that leads to actionable insights.
*	Has an ability to manage multiple projects and stakeholders contemporarily and get them working towards a common goal.
*       Has ability to present and/or tailor communications towards different audiences, from peers to executives.
*       Passionate about coaching and continuous learning. 
*	Has international experience organizing workshops in Europe, US and China.
*	Analytical: strong Excel and Tableau skills.
*      Multilingual: fluent in English, Italian and Polish.
